msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "Sega Twin Stick"
msgstr "Sega Twin Stick"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "The Sega Twin Stick, released in 1996, features two joysticks at the expense of fewer buttons. It was designed for the game Cyber Troopers Virtual-On."
msgstr "Sega Twin Stick, vydaný v roce 1996, má dva joysticky za cenu menšího počtu tlačítek. Byl navržen pro hru Cyber Troopers Virtual-On."

